    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A superpolymer that maintains mechanical and chemical integrity above 400 degrees Fahrenheit for extended periods and has high strength and modulus of elasticity and excellent resistance to solvent, oil, and corrosive environment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000027671/Brady and Clauser, Materials Handbook (1977)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Superpolímero que mantiene su integridad mecánica y química por sobre 400 grados Fahrenheit durante extensos períodos, con alta resistencia y módulo de elasticidad, y excelente resistencia a los solventes, petróleo y ambiente corrosivo.
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een superpolymeer die bij temperaturen boven de 200 graden Celsius voor lange tijd de oorspronkelijke mechanische en chemische toestand aanhoudt; het is zeer sterk en elastisch en is uitstekende bestand tegen oplosmiddelen, olie en corrosieve omstandigheden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>長時間處於華氏四百度以上高溫仍能維持機械和化學完整性之超聚合物，具高強度和彈性模量，抗溶劑、油及腐蝕環境力極佳。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
